%N A397718 Self-convolution of superfactorials (A000178).
%F A397718 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} A000178(k)*A000178(n-k).
%F A397718 a(n) ~ 2^((n+3)/2) * Pi^((n+1)/2) * n^(n^2/2 + n + 5/12) / (A * exp(3*n^2/4 + n - 1/12)), where A is the Glaisher-Kinkelin constant A074962.
%t A397718 Table[Sum[BarnesG[k+2]*BarnesG[n-k+2], {k, 0, n}], {n, 0, 15}]
